query: SELECT op.id as positionId, op.pnl as positionPnl, op.tradeId, t.pnl as tradePnl, op.strategySymbol FROM open_positions op JOIN trades t ON op.tradeId = t.id WHERE op.status = 'closed' AND op.pnl != t.pnl LIMIT 20;
